Interface IDiagnosticFunctionIdentifierInhibit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagnosticCommonElement, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IDiagnosticFunctionIdentifierInhibit
extends IEntity, IDiagnosticCommonElement
    IDiagnosticFunctionIdentifierInhibit: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to define the inhibition of a specific function identifier within the Fim configuration.
